{"tid":830590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】國家主席因急病救治無效逝世（Now新聞台）","createTime":"2018-09-21T09:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T00:00:16.000Z","uid":155095,"like":298,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a78ccdb68c176510a31480c5a154b8e6ac9f14cc","tid":830590,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】越南國營傳媒報道，越南國家主席陳大光病逝，終年61歲。<br />\n<br />\n陳大光本月多次接見外國訪客，包括印尼總統佐科維多多和緬甸國務資政昂山素姬。最後一次公開露面是在前日，會見到訪的中國最高人民法院院長周強和出席共產黨政治局會議。<br />\n<br />\n官方越南通訊社報道，陳大光今早在首都河內的醫院因患有嚴重疾病逝世，國內外醫生和專家救治無效。<br />\n<br />\n陳大光曾任公安部部長和國會代表，2016年當選國家主席，任期五年。<br />\n<br />\n越南以國家主席為國家元首，但越共總書記（阮富仲）才是最高領導人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/2016/1120/07/28/20161120072800939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimg2.huanqiu.com%2Fattachment2010%2F2016%2F1120%2F07%2F28%2F20161120072800939.jpg&h=3e1e0039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/11/GettyImages-872509836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FGettyImages-872509836.jpg&h=cf9e3865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=321090&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321090%26refer%3D&d=UPo%2BapQ%2FltICJJmezQhqlS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=17be41d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321090%26refer%3D&h=ae64d428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=321090&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"aafe8d0361d216d114747883a3f44695def7479f","tid":830590,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hk